data.description: Nearly 5 acres of fenced horse property with a site built metal frame block stucco home!  Home has recently been upgraded with wood-look tile flooring throughout! Spacious bright kitchen, includes all appliances & large breakfast bar w/storage overlooking living room! Primary bedrm & bath have jetted tub, remodeled vanity, walk-in & secondary closets.  Guest bathrm has matching remodeled vanity.  Huge laundry rm connects to primary bath w/door provides privacy.  Key items include: 400' deep well & 2 neighbors pay for water usage, 45x36' concrete slab ready for supersized garage, gravel driveways, storage sheds, new water heater, watersoftner, fans thru out, full covered front patio & 7 pine trees w/irrigation.  All this in quaint Hidden Valley surrounded by mountains!
